# AdVault — Caddy reverse proxy with automatic HTTPS (Let's Encrypt).
# `<ip-with-dashes>.sslip.io` resolves to that IP with zero DNS setup, so Caddy
# can obtain a real TLS cert for a bare-IP host. TLS lets the API's `secure`
# refresh cookie round-trip, so login actually persists.
#
# Replace the hostname with YOUR server IP (dots → dashes). WebSocket upgrades
# (/api/ws/notifications) are proxied transparently by Caddy.
74-0-48-138.sslip.io {
    encode gzip
    reverse_proxy web:80
}
